---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions — Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="SMS/MMS program terms and conditions for Lone Ranger Roofing. Message frequency, opt-out instructions, and carrier information."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-2">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-500 mb-3">SMS/MMS Program Terms &amp; Conditions</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-12">Last updated: June 2025</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Program Description</h2>
          <p>When you opt in, you will receive text messages (SMS/MMS) from Lone Ranger Roofing to your mobile number. These messages may include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1 text-gray-600">
            <li>Responses to quote or estimate requests</li>
            <li>Real-time communication about services and pricing</li>
            <li>Appointment scheduling and confirmations</li>
            <li>Project updates</li>
            <li>Follow-up messages</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Message Frequency</h2>
          <p>You can expect to receive approximately 5–10 messages per month based on your project needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Opt-Out</h2>
          <p>You can cancel SMS at any time. Text <strong>STOP</strong> to the number you received messages from. After texting STOP, we will send a confirmation that you have been unsubscribed. You will receive no further messages. To re-subscribe, sign up again through our website form or text <strong>START</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Help</h2>
          <p>If you experience issues, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message or contact us directly at <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline font-semibold">(254) 300-1413</a> or <a href="mailto:info@lonerangerroofing.com" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline font-semibold">info@lonerangerroofing.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Carrier Liability</h2>
          <p>Carriers such as AT&amp;T, Verizon, and T-Mobile are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Message and Data Rates</h2>
          <p>Message and data rates may apply for messages sent to and from us. Contact your wireless provider with questions about your plan.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Privacy</h2>
          <p>For questions about how we handle your personal information, please read our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline font-semibold">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Consent Not Required for Purchase</h2>
          <p>Consent to receive SMS messages is not a condition of purchasing any service from Lone Ranger Roofing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <address class="not-italic space-y-1 text-gray-600">
            <p class="font-bold text-brand-900">Lone Ranger Roofing, LLC</p>
            <p>715 E Downs Ave, Temple, TX 76501</p>
            <p><a href="tel:+12543001413" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">(254) 300-1413</a></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:lonerangerroofingtx@gmail.com" class="text-accent-600 hover:underline">lonerangerroofingtx@gmail.com</a></p>
          </address>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
